body_html:
What's the version of glibc on your machine? (can probably run ldd --version to find out)

This is likely because you don't have glibc 2.17 installed, but our precompiled binary expects it. You could build from source to let it pick up the version of glibc you have on your machine.

body:
What's the version of glibc on your machine? (can probably run `ldd --version` to find out)

This is likely because you don't have glibc 2.17 installed, but our precompiled binary expects it. You could build from source to let it pick up the version of glibc you have on your machine.
